2.0.1.name: wordpress/lanoba-social
2.0.1.description:
Log in and share from a choice of multiple social accounts like Facebook, Twitter, Google and LinkedIn among others. With fewer passwords and logins to remember, the browsing experience is positive, registration simple and sharing faster.

Lanoba is FREE for all websites with under 5000 users. All websites, even those with 5000 users and less enjoy all of Lanoba’s features, including access to advanced analytics, data storage, exporting and extended profile data.

Login

  • Enable social login for all your new and existing users
  • Map existing user accounts to their social accounts
  • Supports Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn, Yahoo, Google, MySpace, Foursquare, Salesforce & Windows Live

Sharing

  • Share to multiple networks simultaneously
  • Auto-trigger shares

Data

  • Data storage
  • Data exporting
